    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Order Domain represents discipline, as well as devotion to the laws that govern a society, an institution, or a philosophy. Clerics of Order meditate on logic and justice as they serve their gods, examples of which appear in the Order Deities table.</p>\n<p>Clerics of Order believe that well-crafted laws establish legitimate hierarchies, and those selected by law to lead must be obeyed. Those who obey must do so to the best of their ability, and if those who lead fail to protect the law, they must be replaced. In this manner, law weaves a web of obligations that create order and security in a chaotic multiverse.</p>\n<h3>Order Domain Spells</h3>\n<table>\n<thead style=\"text-shadow:1px 1px var(--color-shadow-dark);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\">\n<tr>\n<td>Cleric Level</td>\n<td>Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.UFyMGkLPBAGvdsvO]{Command}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.z5Obqs7xTmWLLcis]{Heroism}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.NXOXaNWD6HazQkmY]{Hold Person}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.NRjio9BELvgzdSgt]{Zone of Truth}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.lFSThD582H4mzi5k]{Mass Healing Word}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.ZYKGI9wbcusyCtkF]{Slow}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.0p0GzWMBQOYfX9hj]{Compulsion}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.es04c1GiG2bGlCUz]{Locate Creature}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.36N9teHyOrCiu4vZ]{Commune}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.vZVDWUj69cLI1Qhz]{Dominate Person}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Order Domain Features</h3>\n<p>1st Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.vcgCYAK7rqHfcgx6]{Bonus Proficiencies}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.bZat0oZKX0AiTd11]{Voice of Authority}</p>\n<p>2nd Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.BJyoQly5Sx67LMFk]{Channel Divinity: Order's Demand}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.Sj1FeRHRnRe0bkm3]{Embodiment of the Law}</p>\n<p>8th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.vfbfWtXhJ2CkCDSo]{Divine Strike}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.bHyP9gqdYHSpmnXz]{Order's Wrath}</p>",
